column4: On campus is specified as a person's residency arrangement as defined in the Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA).
Off campus, with family is specified as a person's residency arrangement as defined in the Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA).
Off campus, without family is specified as a person's residency arrangement as defined in the Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA).
A person's residency arrangement is unknown as defined in the Free Application for Federal Student Aid (FAFSA).
